---
import Layout from "C:/Users/Owner/tchsaero-site/src/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Home | TCHS Aero" active="home">
  <!-- text + image -->
  <section class="not-prose grid items-center gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">
        Let&apos;s revolutionize flight.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
        We are TCHS Aero, an aspiring team of student engineers, coders, and creators from Temple City High School.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-blue-900 px-5 py-3 text-white font-semibold hover:opacity-90"
          href="/about"
        >
          Learn more about us →
        </a>
        <a
          class="inline-block rounded-lg border border-gray-300 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-blue-900 hover:bg-gray-50"
          href="/contact"
        >
          Contact →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Put your image in: public/images/hero.jpg -->
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-100">
      <img
        src="/images/hero.jpg"
        alt="TCHS Aero team / drone"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <h2>Our Story.</h2>
  <p>
    Our team is working together to merge flight and artificial intelligence to create an optimized automated drone
    for the college-level SUAS competition in June 2026.
  </p>
  <p>
    Since the summer of 2024, we&apos;ve been laying the groundwork by testing budgets, analyzing the difficulty of our craft,
    and planning our team structure. Now, we&apos;re ready to recruit and make TCHS Aero official.
  </p>

  <!-- PHOTO + TEXT COLUMN SECTION (Google Sites blocks) -->
  <section class="not-prose mt-10 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-100">
      <img
        src="/images/section1.jpg"
        alt="Drone build / workshop"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">Hands-on innovation</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">
        Students learn real engineering workflows: mechanical design, electronics integration, autonomy software,
        testing, and iteration.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">
        We organize into Programming, Mechanical/Electrical, and Operations so everyone can contribute.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Alternating image/text (reverse on desktop) -->
  <section class="not-prose mt-10 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
    <div class="md:order-2 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-100">
      <img
        src="/images/section2.jpg"
        alt="Flight testing"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="md:order-1">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">Competing at the collegiate level</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">
        We&apos;re preparing for SUAS — a competition that challenges teams to build autonomous drones and complete mission tasks.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">
        It&apos;s a chance to gain experience and represent our school on a bigger stage.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <h3 class="mt-12">QUICK Q&amp;A</h3>

  <section class="not-prose mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6">
      <h4 class="text-lg font-bold">What is TCHS Aero?</h4>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
        TCHS Aero is Temple City High School’s autonomous drone team. We design, build, and program AI-powered drones.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6">
      <h4 class="text-lg font-bold">Who can join the team?</h4>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
        Students passionate about STEM — coding, mechanical design, electronics, media, or operations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6">
      <h4 class="text-lg font-bold">What are the sub-teams?</h4>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
        Programming (AI + autonomy), Mechanical/Electrical (build + integrate), Operations (outreach + logistics).
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6">
      <h4 class="text-lg font-bold">How can I support the team?</h4>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
        Sponsorships and donations. Visit the Sponsor page or email
        <a class="text-blue-900 font-semibold hover:underline" href="mailto:tchsaero@tcusd.net">tchsaero@tcusd.net</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
